OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778602268
OL,3,CThousands of young people brave
OL,4,CDartmoor for Ten Tors Challenge
OL,6,FAround 2,400 young people embark on
OL,7,Fthis year's Ten Tors Challenge on
OL,8,FDartmoor.
OL,10,FThousands of young people will brave
OL,11,Fthe wilds of Dartmoor this weekend to
OL,12,Fcomplete the gruelling Ten Tors
OL,13,FChallenge.
OL,15,FThey set out in teams of six, tackling
OL,16,Fa 35-, 45- or 55-mile route, camping
OL,17,Fovernight on the moor, and
OL,18,Fencountering some of the toughest
OL,19,Fterrain in southern England.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
