CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778602268
OL,3,CThousands of young people brave
OL,4,CDartmoor for Ten Tors Challenge
OL,6,FThe challenge started at 7am on
OL,7,FSaturday 9 May and the teams will rely
OL,8,Fon their navigational skills and carry
OL,9,Fall their food, water, bedding, tents,
OL,10,Fand essentials as they go.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, youngsters with special
OL,13,Feducational needs and disabilities can
OL,14,Ftake on the one-day Jubilee Challenge
OL,15,For overnight Granite Challenge -
OL,16,Fpreviously known as the Jubilee
OL,17,FChallenge Plus.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
