PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778602268
OL,3,CThousands of young people brave
OL,4,CDartmoor for Ten Tors Challenge
OL,6,FThe annual event is run by the
OL,7,Fmilitary, and doubles as a high-level
OL,8,Fresilience operation, called Exercise
OL,9,FWyvern Tor.
OL,11,FColonel Jon Penhale, South West
OL,12,FAssistant Commander took on the Ten
OL,13,FTors as a boy and said, for him, it
OL,14,Fwas a defining moment.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
