OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778602268
OL,3,CThousands of young people brave
OL,4,CDartmoor for Ten Tors Challenge
OL,6,F"When I was at school in
OL,7,FGloucestershire, I had the pleasure of
OL,8,Fdoing both 35- and 45-mile routes and
OL,9,Fso as a young person enjoying this
OL,10,Fevent, it very much shaped me and set
OL,11,Fme on a course to think about
OL,12,F'actually, I really enjoy it'.
OL,14,F"I enjoyed what it gave me in terms of
OL,15,Fleadership and resilience and as a
OL,16,Fresult of that after university I
OL,17,Fjoined the Army," he said.
OL,19,FColonel Jon Penhale tells ITV News'
OL,20,FCharlie Powell what the Ten Tors means
OL,21,Fto him.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
