FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778602268
OL,3,CThousands of young people brave
OL,4,CDartmoor for Ten Tors Challenge
OL,6,FTo mark the start of this year's
OL,7,Fchallenge, the British Army's famous
OL,8,Fparachute display team, the Red
OL,9,FDevils, jumped into Okehampton Camp.
OL,11,FA total of 2,400 young people aged
OL,12,Fbetween 14 and 19 will take part in
OL,13,FTen Tors, with a further 400 taking
OL,14,Fpart in the Jubilee Challenge, many in
OL,15,Fwheelchairs, over routes of up to 15
OL,16,Fmiles.
OL,18,FThe majority of the teams who enter
OL,19,FTen Tors are from schools and youth
OL,20,Fgroups from across the South West.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
