FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778602268
OL,3,CThousands of young people brave
OL,4,CDartmoor for Ten Tors Challenge
OL,6,FThese include scout groups, sports and
OL,7,Framblers' teams and Armed Forces cadet
OL,8,Funits.
OL,10,FThis year's Dartmoor Granite Challenge
OL,11,Fis aimed at young adults with Special
OL,12,FEducational Needs and Disability
OL,13,F(SEND) who are capable of an overnight
OL,14,Fstay but may find the Ten Tors
OL,15,FChallenge too inaccessible due to
OL,16,Ftheir respective SEND.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
