OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1778602268
OL,3,CThousands of young people brave
OL,4,CDartmoor for Ten Tors Challenge
OL,6,FIt provides an appropriately arduous
OL,7,Fchallenge across difficult terrain and
OL,8,Fin very changeable weather over at
OL,9,Fleast 11 miles, including an overnight
OL,10,Fcamp.
OL,12,FThe challenge is planned by the
OL,13,FBritish Army's Headquarters South West
OL,14,Fmonths in advance working with other
OL,15,Forganisations, such as Devon and
OL,16,FCornwall Police, the Met Office, the
OL,17,FBritish Red Cross and the Dartmoor
OL,18,FSearch and Rescue Group, who will
OL,19,Fprovide almost 350 volunteers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
